OL,3,CHottest day of the year expected
OL,4,Cbefore thunderstorms end fine weather
OL,6,FSunday is likely to be the warmest day
OL,7,Fof the year so far, before
OL,8,Fthunderstorms and heavy rain put an
OL,9,Fend to a week of sunshine, the Met
OL,10,FOffice has said.
OL,12,FWhilst the hottest temperatures of the
OL,13,Fyear so far were recorded on Saturday,
OL,14,FSimon Partridge, a meteorologist at
OL,15,Fthe Met Office, said the records were
OL,16,F"not likely to last long" as
OL,17,Fforecasters expect it to be even
OL,18,Fwarmer on Sunday.
