OL,3,CHottest day of the year expected
OL,4,Cbefore thunderstorms end fine weather
OL,6,FThere are three yellow thunderstorm
OL,7,Fwarnings in place on Sunday.
OL,9,FOne covers most areas of the west of
OL,10,Fthe UK, including the majority of
OL,11,FWales, where thunderstorms are
OL,12,Fexpected between midday and 10pm.
OL,14,FThe second is for the western half of
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland between 11am and 7pm.
OL,17,FThe third is for western parts of
OL,18,FScotland between 2pm on Sunday to 4am
OL,19,Fon Monday. Mr Partridge said this
OL,20,Fwarning is slightly different as more
OL,21,Fsignificant rainfall is expected.
