OL,3,CHottest day of the year expected
OL,4,Cbefore thunderstorms end fine weather
OL,6,FPeople in areas with a yellow warning
OL,7,Fshould expect some disruption,
OL,8,Fespecially to travel.
OL,10,FSpray and sudden flooding could lead
OL,11,Fto difficult driving conditions and
OL,12,Fthere is a slight chance of power
OL,13,Fcuts, the Met Office said.
OL,15,FOn Saturday, temperatures peaked at
OL,16,F25.9C in Herstmonceux, East Sussex,
OL,17,Fand in northern Scotland a temperature
OL,18,Fof 25.7C was recorded in Cassley.
