OL,6,FOn Friday, 17-year-old Ronalds Abele
OL,7,Fdied after getting into difficulty
OL,8,Fwhile swimming at the Embankment, in
OL,9,FWellingborough, and was pulled from
OL,10,Fthe water by emergency services,
OL,11,FNorthamptonshire Police said.
OL,13,FHe was pronounced dead in hospital.
